data.title: Lake Geneva Schools
data.meta_description: Lake Geneva Schools is comprised of two districts – Lake Geneva Joint #1 Schools and Lake Geneva-Genoa City Union (Badger) High School. Our long-standing tradition of excellence is made possible through close collaboration between our community, families, and staff. At Lake Geneva Schools, our students benefit from our big school opportunities and small school strengths. We invite you to explore everything we have to offer! Our Mission Engage. Educate. Empower. Our Vision Creating and connecting opportunities for excellence.
